00:31.320 --> 00:34.480
<font color="#ffffff">We speak of the</font>
<font color="#ffffff">dawn of a new day</font>

00:34.480 --> 00:37.160
<font color="#ffffff">as though it is</font>
<font color="#ffffff">a wholly welcome thing.</font>

00:39.240 --> 00:42.880
<font color="#ffffff">But there are times when dawn</font>
<font color="#ffffff">breaks into darkness...</font>

00:44.600 --> 00:47.920
<font color="#ffffff">..forcing us to face the things</font>
<font color="#ffffff">we never knew we'd see.</font>

00:53.200 --> 00:56.200
<font color="#ffffff">DOOR OPENS</font>

01:02.720 --> 01:03.960
<font color="#ffffff">Cup of tea for you.</font>

01:05.400 --> 01:07.360
<font color="#ffffff">Drink it while it's hot.</font>

01:07.360 --> 01:09.520
<font color="#ffff00">This time last year there</font>
<font color="#ffff00">was a wedding dress</font>

01:09.520 --> 01:10.920
<font color="#ffff00">hanging from that picture rail.</font>

01:28.040 --> 01:33.280
<font color="#00ff00">What I said to you when we arrived</font>
<font color="#00ff00">in South Africa still holds good.</font>

01:33.280 --> 01:37.200
<font color="#00ff00">There are three things you need</font>
<font color="#00ff00">when you arrive in a foreign</font>

01:37.200 --> 01:40.640
<font color="#00ff00">country - a scrub-up, a shave</font>
<font color="#00ff00">and a visit to the khazi.</font>

01:40.640 --> 01:42.800
<font color="#ffffff">I'm not in a foreign country, Fred.</font>

01:42.800 --> 01:44.440
<font color="#ffffff">I'm in my own home.</font>

01:44.440 --> 01:46.400
<font color="#ffffff">In a place where I've</font>
<font color="#ffffff">lived for years.</font>

01:48.800 --> 01:50.400
<font color="#ffffff">It just, er...</font>
<font color="#00ff00">It feels like somewhere</font>

01:50.400 --> 01:51.760
<font color="#00ff00">where you've never been before.</font>

01:55.280 --> 01:58.920
<font color="#00ff00">Now, you're big enough and ugly</font>
<font color="#00ff00">enough to make your own khazi</font>

01:58.920 --> 02:00.560
<font color="#00ff00">and scrub-up arrangements.</font>

02:00.560 --> 02:02.760
<font color="#00ff00">The shave you need to leave to me.</font>

02:05.680 --> 02:09.000
<font color="#ffffff">We recount old beats</font>
<font color="#ffffff">of other stories.</font>

02:10.520 --> 02:17.320
<font color="#ffffff">We retrace our steps, take refuge</font>
<font color="#ffffff">in echoes of that which is familiar.</font>

02:18.840 --> 02:23.080
<font color="#ffffff">We follow custom and ritual</font>
<font color="#ffffff">because we have no map.</font>

02:24.080 --> 02:26.960
<font color="#ffffff">We reach out blindly.</font>

02:28.480 --> 02:33.160
<font color="#ffffff">We cannot see the path</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and, far from home,</font>

02:33.160 --> 02:36.800
<font color="#ffffff">we cling to the way these</font>
<font color="#ffffff">things are always done.</font>

02:39.840 --> 02:42.200
<font color="#00ffff"># Be still my soul</font>

02:43.600 --> 02:50.240
<font color="#00ffff"># When change and tears are past</font>

02:50.240 --> 02:54.200
<font color="#00ffff"># All safe and blessed</font>

02:54.200 --> 03:01.880
<font color="#00ffff"># And we shall meet at last. #</font>

03:03.600 --> 03:04.840
<font color="#ffff00">Please be seated.</font>

03:09.000 --> 03:11.640
<font color="#ffff00">Before we move out into the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">churchyard for the committal</font>

03:11.640 --> 03:16.200
<font color="#ffff00">proceedings, Barbara's great friend</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and colleague Phyllis Crane</font>

03:16.200 --> 03:19.720
<font color="#ffff00">will read a short poem to help us</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to gather our thoughts.</font>

03:43.200 --> 03:45.560
<font color="#ffffff">BABY CRIES</font>

03:47.200 --> 03:50.720
<font color="#00ffff">Sorry. </font><font color="#ffffff">Oh. Please don't</font>
<font color="#ffffff">take the little one out.</font>

03:51.680 --> 03:54.920
<font color="#ffffff">None of us objects to the</font>
<font color="#ffffff">sound of a crying child.</font>

04:04.360 --> 04:08.760
<font color="#ffffff">"If I should die</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and leave you here awhile,</font>

04:08.760 --> 04:12.480
<font color="#ffffff">"be not like others sore</font>
<font color="#ffffff">undone, who keep</font>

04:12.480 --> 04:15.680
<font color="#ffffff">"long vigils by the silent</font>
<font color="#ffffff">dust, and weep."</font>

04:18.040 --> 04:22.280
<font color="#ffffff">"For my sake - turn again to life</font>

04:22.280 --> 04:23.600
<font color="#ffffff">"and smile..."</font>

04:28.320 --> 04:33.160
<font color="#ffffff">"..nerving thy heart</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and trembling hand to do</font>

04:33.160 --> 04:37.080
<font color="#ffffff">"something to comfort weaker</font>
<font color="#ffffff">hearts than thine."</font>

04:41.640 --> 04:45.960
<font color="#ffffff">"Complete these dear</font>
<font color="#ffffff">unfinished tasks of mine</font>

04:45.960 --> 04:49.680
<font color="#ffffff">"and I, perchance may</font>
<font color="#ffffff">therein comfort you."</font>

05:00.560 --> 05:02.480
<font color="#00ff00">Vi? </font><font color="#ffff00">No, thank you.</font>

05:06.640 --> 05:08.400
<font color="#00ff00">What's happened to Phyllis?</font>

05:08.400 --> 05:11.120
<font color="#00ffff">She said she was going upstairs</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to get changed.</font>

05:11.120 --> 05:13.160
<font color="#ffffff">BELL RINGS</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Oh.</font>

05:13.160 --> 05:14.280
<font color="#00ff00">Off you pop.</font>

05:15.800 --> 05:18.120
<font color="#ffffff">DOOR OPENS</font>

05:20.240 --> 05:23.040
<font color="#00ffff">I've been called out to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a Mrs Olive Mawson.</font>

05:23.040 --> 05:25.640
<font color="#00ffff">Nine months along, staying</font>
<font color="#00ffff">with family in the district.</font>

05:33.760 --> 05:37.000
<font color="#00ffff">Are you going to go</font>
<font color="#00ffff">downstairs, Phyllis?</font>

05:37.000 --> 05:40.800
<font color="#ffffff">I've never found grief and a cold</font>
<font color="#ffffff">spread to be an easy combination.</font>

05:43.320 --> 05:45.800
<font color="#ffffff">The service itself is trial enough.</font>

05:45.800 --> 05:49.360
<font color="#00ffff">Your reading gave people a</font>
<font color="#00ffff">great deal of comfort.</font>

05:50.560 --> 05:52.520
<font color="#ffffff">Tom chose it.</font>

05:52.520 --> 05:53.760
<font color="#ffffff">It seemed apt.</font>

05:55.280 --> 05:56.800
<font color="#ffffff">We've got work to do, haven't we?</font>

05:59.520 --> 06:01.080
<font color="#ffffff">The world doesn't stop.</font>

06:10.040 --> 06:11.480
<font color="#00ff00">Has it started?</font>

06:11.480 --> 06:14.200
<font color="#00ffff">Your daughter's fine</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for now, Mr Hodgkiss.</font>

06:14.200 --> 06:15.440
<font color="#00ffff">You can go to work.</font>

06:16.880 --> 06:19.240
<font color="#00ffff">Go.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">OLIVE WHIMPERS</font>

06:21.600 --> 06:25.400
<font color="#00ffff">They're what we call Braxton Hicks</font>
<font color="#00ffff">contractions, precious. </font><font color="#ffffff">Mm.</font>

06:25.400 --> 06:30.160
<font color="#00ffff">You have to think of it as Mother</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Nature tuning up her orchestra.</font>

06:30.160 --> 06:31.680
<font color="#00ffff">Try to relax a little.</font>

06:31.680 --> 06:34.280
<font color="#ffffff">I thought I'd feel calmer</font>
<font color="#ffffff">when I moved back in with my dad.</font>

06:36.240 --> 06:40.120
<font color="#00ffff">How about I make a cup of tea</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and you tell me why you did that?</font>

06:41.600 --> 06:44.440
<font color="#ffffff">DOOR CREAKS</font>
<font color="#ffff00">We're lucky the funeral didn't clash</font>

06:44.440 --> 06:46.360
<font color="#ffff00">with Angela's birthday party,</font>

06:46.360 --> 06:50.760
<font color="#ffff00">but I've still got my work cut out</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to get everything done by tomorrow.</font>

06:50.760 --> 06:53.800
<font color="#00ff00">Can't you just buy it</font>
<font color="#00ff00">all from a shop?</font>

06:53.800 --> 06:58.040
<font color="#ffff00">We have to get back to the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">business of life, Patrick.</font>

06:58.040 --> 07:00.960
<font color="#ffff00">And everything else, it's the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">opposite of the pain and the grief</font>

07:00.960 --> 07:02.160
<font color="#ffff00">and the loss we saw today.</font>

07:03.600 --> 07:06.960
<font color="#ffff00">I feel as though I'll drown if</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I don't do something positive.</font>

07:08.400 --> 07:09.600
<font color="#00ff00">Can I help?</font>

07:14.240 --> 07:17.400
<font color="#ffff00">You can pass me things down</font>
<font color="#ffff00">off the high shelves.</font>

07:17.400 --> 07:22.200
<font color="#ffff00">Starting with the bunny blancmange</font>
<font color="#ffff00">mould and my piping nozzles.</font>

07:22.200 --> 07:25.520
<font color="#ffff00">Then go and change your tie before</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you head back to the surgery.</font>

07:29.280 --> 07:30.960
<font color="#ffffff">My husband...</font>

07:30.960 --> 07:33.240
<font color="#ffffff">was seeing another woman.</font>

07:33.240 --> 07:34.640
<font color="#ffffff">I turned a blind eye.</font>

07:36.960 --> 07:39.800
<font color="#ffffff">It was easy enough,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">as long as I ignored it.</font>

07:39.800 --> 07:41.600
<font color="#ffffff">But then I couldn't ignore it...</font>
<font color="#ffffff">BELL RINGS</font>

07:41.600 --> 07:42.640
<font color="#ffffff">..any longer.</font>

07:43.720 --> 07:44.800
<font color="#ffffff">Excuse me.</font>

07:48.520 --> 07:50.160
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, hello, Uncle Donald.</font>

07:51.560 --> 07:52.920
<font color="#00ff00">Ironing service.</font>

07:52.920 --> 07:56.480
<font color="#ffffff">Dad's already gone to work.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">You done his shirt for today.</font>

07:56.480 --> 07:59.000
<font color="#00ff00">Well, he...he'll need</font>
<font color="#00ff00">a clean one tomorrow.</font>

08:09.200 --> 08:10.280
<font color="#ffffff">Sorry, Nurse.</font>

08:10.280 --> 08:12.560
<font color="#ffffff">Unexpected visitor.</font>

08:12.560 --> 08:14.480
<font color="#ffffff">The laundry basket's on</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the draining board.</font>

08:18.320 --> 08:20.560
<font color="#ffffff">Uncle Donald was in the Navy.</font>

08:20.560 --> 08:22.440
<font color="#ffffff">Makes men quite handy,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">life at sea.</font>

08:24.440 --> 08:26.600
<font color="#ffffff">FOOTSTEPS APPROACH</font>

08:32.120 --> 08:33.360
<font color="#00ffff">Mr Hereward.</font>

08:35.080 --> 08:38.360
<font color="#00ffff">Your parents say they're</font>
<font color="#00ffff">ready to leave when you are.</font>

08:38.360 --> 08:40.240
<font color="#ffffff">I'm not sure I want to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">go with them now.</font>

08:45.720 --> 08:48.800
<font color="#00ffff">I think it might be preferable</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to spending time alone.</font>

08:50.280 --> 08:52.680
<font color="#ffffff">I've got years to do</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that, haven't I?</font>

08:55.320 --> 08:59.840
<font color="#ffffff">Did you know that Barbara's</font>
<font color="#ffffff">name is still on the call</font>

08:59.840 --> 09:01.240
<font color="#ffffff">board in the clinical room?</font>

09:06.280 --> 09:08.840
<font color="#ffffff">Chalk doesn't rub out as</font>
<font color="#ffffff">completely as you think.</font>

09:17.360 --> 09:19.000
<font color="#ffffff">I'll go with my parents.</font>

09:20.160 --> 09:21.560
<font color="#ffffff">And next week I will come back...</font>

09:23.760 --> 09:24.960
<font color="#ffffff">..and I will start again.</font>

09:36.840 --> 09:38.920
<font color="#ffffff">SHE SIGHS</font>

09:43.960 --> 09:47.240
<font color="#ffff00">Why...won't you...work?</font>

09:49.480 --> 09:52.600
<font color="#ffff00">I cannot obtain access to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the television news.</font>

09:56.120 --> 09:58.520
<font color="#ffff00">Have the angels abandoned us</font>
<font color="#ffff00">completely?</font>

10:34.960 --> 10:37.280
<font color="#ffffff">CHILDREN CHEER</font>

10:58.720 --> 11:00.840
<font color="#ffffff">SHE GASPS</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Ready?</font>

11:01.960 --> 11:04.400
<font color="#ffff00">And wait for Daddy to say when.</font>

11:04.400 --> 11:05.680
<font color="#00ff00">One, two...</font>

11:05.680 --> 11:08.560
<font color="#ffffff">PHONE RINGS</font>
<font color="#00ff00">..three - NOW!</font>

11:11.800 --> 11:12.960
<font color="#ffff00">Sorry.</font>

11:15.520 --> 11:18.080
<font color="#00ff00">Come on, everyone!</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Let's try that again.</font>

11:18.080 --> 11:19.840
<font color="#ffffff">Dad, can I have a go?</font>

11:22.160 --> 11:26.120
<font color="#ffff00">Indeed! My response would be</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to say that I find your attitude</font>

11:26.120 --> 11:27.880
<font color="#ffff00">highly presumptuous.</font>

11:27.880 --> 11:31.560
<font color="#ffff00">And that you won't receive</font>
<font color="#ffff00">an answer from this practice</font>

11:31.560 --> 11:33.760
<font color="#ffff00">until the matter's been</font>
<font color="#ffff00">discussed with Dr Turner.</font>

11:33.760 --> 11:35.520
<font color="#00ff00">Have I been called out?</font>

11:35.520 --> 11:38.200
<font color="#ffff00">No. That was the Officer for Health,</font>

11:38.200 --> 11:41.160
<font color="#ffff00">needing to speak urgently,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and informing us</font>

11:41.160 --> 11:44.000
<font color="#ffff00">that Warkworth Street maternity</font>
<font color="#ffff00">home is to be closed down.</font>

11:44.000 --> 11:47.240
<font color="#00ff00">Still, Dr Gillies should have been</font>
<font color="#00ff00">put out to pasture years ago.</font>

11:47.240 --> 11:49.960
<font color="#ffff00">He's apparently moving to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">a modernised group practice</font>

11:49.960 --> 11:53.000
<font color="#ffff00">in Lewisham and most</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of his patients, including his</font>

11:53.000 --> 11:56.080
<font color="#ffff00">mothers-to-be, are being referred</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to us with immediate effect.</font>

11:56.080 --> 11:59.560
<font color="#00ff00">Shelagh, our maternity home</font>
<font color="#00ff00">has only got four beds.</font>

12:00.760 --> 12:03.200
<font color="#ffff00">The children are going to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">finish their jelly and cream</font>

12:03.200 --> 12:05.920
<font color="#ffff00">and have a lovely game</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of oranges and lemons,</font>

12:05.920 --> 12:07.440
<font color="#ffff00">then we'll come up with a plan.</font>

12:12.480 --> 12:14.520
<font color="#ffffff">ALARM RINGS</font>

12:18.360 --> 12:19.600
<font color="#ffffff">Oh.</font>

12:20.960 --> 12:22.480
<font color="#00ff00">Something the matter, Phyllis?</font>

12:22.480 --> 12:23.600
<font color="#ffffff">My back.</font>

12:25.160 --> 12:27.080
<font color="#ffffff">I thought I felt something go</font>

12:27.080 --> 12:30.120
<font color="#ffffff">when I bent down to pick up</font>
<font color="#ffffff">some soil beside the grave.</font>

12:32.480 --> 12:35.040
<font color="#00ffff">If we were to take on this caseload,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">it means that there would be</font>

12:35.040 --> 12:39.120
<font color="#00ffff">more than 30 extra babies</font>
<font color="#00ffff">due in the next month alone.</font>

12:39.120 --> 12:41.840
<font color="#ffffff">Dare I ask whether</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Warkworth Street have</font>

12:41.840 --> 12:45.920
<font color="#ffffff">passed on details of all</font>
<font color="#ffffff">their discarded patients?</font>

12:45.920 --> 12:48.280
<font color="#ffff00">Unfortunately, no.</font>

12:48.280 --> 12:49.600
<font color="#ffff00">But we do have this.</font>

12:51.560 --> 12:54.240
<font color="#00ff00">Ooh, would you like me to fetch</font>
<font color="#00ff00">you some embrocation, Nurse Crane?</font>

12:54.240 --> 12:56.240
<font color="#ffffff">No, I would not!</font>

12:56.240 --> 12:58.040
<font color="#ffffff">I would like you</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and your colleagues</font>

12:58.040 --> 13:01.640
<font color="#ffffff">to put together as many additional</font>
<font color="#ffffff">home-delivery packs as we may</font>

13:01.640 --> 13:05.080
<font color="#ffffff">now require and await</font>
<font color="#ffffff">further instructions.</font>

13:05.080 --> 13:06.320
<font color="#00ffff">Yes, Nurse Crane.</font>

13:07.880 --> 13:10.640
<font color="#ffffff">FOOTSTEPS APPROACH</font>

13:10.640 --> 13:12.960
<font color="#ffffff">Hello, er, television repairs.</font>

13:13.880 --> 13:17.000
<font color="#ffffff">I've had reports of ghosting</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and a very loud whistle.</font>

13:23.120 --> 13:25.120
<font color="#ffffff">I take it you've tried</font>
<font color="#ffffff">wiggling the aerial?</font>

13:25.120 --> 13:27.320
<font color="#00ffff">I haven't tried any remedy at all.</font>

13:27.320 --> 13:30.720
<font color="#ffff00">Your mind has been fixed on</font>
<font color="#ffff00">matters of great sadness.</font>

13:30.720 --> 13:35.040
<font color="#ffff00">But our young friend has passed</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to a better place than this</font>

13:35.040 --> 13:39.440
<font color="#ffff00">and leaves behind a world</font>
<font color="#ffff00">more in need of prayer than ever.</font>

13:39.440 --> 13:42.120
<font color="#ffff00">That is why I require untrammelled</font>

13:42.120 --> 13:44.760
<font color="#ffff00">access to the television news,</font>

13:44.760 --> 13:47.480
<font color="#ffff00">so that we know who to pray for.</font>

13:47.480 --> 13:49.120
<font color="#ffffff">I wish you luck with that.</font>

13:49.120 --> 13:50.680
<font color="#ffffff">Your cathode ray tube's gone.</font>

13:59.720 --> 14:00.800
<font color="#ffff00">Oh.</font>

14:16.960 --> 14:20.000
<font color="#ffffff">HE CLEARS THROAT</font>

14:20.000 --> 14:23.120
<font color="#00ffff">I'm afraid you're</font>
<font color="#00ffff">slightly early, madam.</font>

14:23.120 --> 14:25.360
<font color="#00ffff">Has anyone taken your ticket?</font>

14:25.360 --> 14:30.680
<font color="#ffff00">I surmise you're what is</font>
<font color="#ffff00">known as the commissionaire.</font>

14:30.680 --> 14:32.560
<font color="#00ffff">No, I'm the projectionist.</font>

14:34.960 --> 14:38.600
<font color="#ffff00">Please be advised that</font>
<font color="#ffff00">my interest is entirely</font>

14:38.600 --> 14:40.360
<font color="#ffff00">confined to the news reel,</font>

14:40.360 --> 14:42.720
<font color="#ffff00">which is surely a public service</font>

14:42.720 --> 14:44.920
<font color="#ffff00">and therefore complimentary?</font>

14:44.920 --> 14:47.320
<font color="#00ffff">It's generally considered</font>
<font color="#00ffff">complimentary,</font>

14:47.320 --> 14:49.920
<font color="#00ffff">as long as you've paid</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to see the main attraction.</font>

14:49.920 --> 14:51.200
<font color="#ffff00">What is that?</font>

14:51.200 --> 14:53.480
<font color="#00ffff">It's A Mad, Mad, Mad, Mad World.</font>

14:54.440 --> 14:57.520
<font color="#ffff00">A philosophical treatise, perhaps.</font>

14:57.520 --> 15:01.320
<font color="#ffff00">I'm sure my order will</font>
<font color="#ffff00">pose no objection.</font>

15:03.640 --> 15:06.280
<font color="#00ffff">My daughter Olive's under your</font>
<font color="#00ffff">midwives at the moment.</font>

15:06.280 --> 15:09.360
<font color="#ffff00">Oh. </font><font color="#00ffff">Hm! I'll see you're provided</font>
<font color="#00ffff">with refreshments.</font>

15:09.360 --> 15:11.880
<font color="#ffffff">HE CHUCKLES</font>

15:16.720 --> 15:21.280
<font color="#ffffff">Perfect! This is just the right time</font>
<font color="#ffffff">of year for planting tulips.</font>

15:21.280 --> 15:24.360
<font color="#ffffff">You see, the soil's cold,</font>

15:24.360 --> 15:26.640
<font color="#ffffff">so the bulbs don't get</font>
<font color="#ffffff">bothered by the fungus</font>

15:26.640 --> 15:29.840
<font color="#ffffff">and all them creepy-crawlies</font>
<font color="#ffffff">in the soil.</font>

15:29.840 --> 15:32.160
<font color="#ffffff">Your mum's going to love these.</font>

15:32.160 --> 15:34.120
<font color="#00ff00">Nurse Barbara looks lonely.</font>

15:42.720 --> 15:46.560
<font color="#ffffff">No. She's got your mum to keep</font>
<font color="#ffffff">her company, hasn't she?</font>

15:46.560 --> 15:48.880
<font color="#00ff00">But my mum was old.</font>

15:53.920 --> 15:56.800
<font color="#00ffff">The latest fashion, that's what</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Kathy Victoria's looking for,</font>

15:56.800 --> 15:59.760
<font color="#00ffff">but quite frankly that speckled</font>
<font color="#00ffff">toffee and cream ensemble</font>

15:59.760 --> 16:01.000
<font color="#00ffff">doesn't seem to make it.</font>

16:01.000 --> 16:03.480
<font color="#00ffff">It's too thick to lie flat</font>
<font color="#00ffff">enough with a double fold.</font>

16:10.400 --> 16:13.520
<font color="#00ffff">And here's where the newest</font>
<font color="#00ffff">fashion trick...</font>

16:13.520 --> 16:15.720
<font color="#ffff00">Good afternoon, ladies.</font>

16:15.720 --> 16:18.960
<font color="#ffff00">We'll be running things</font>
